      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "d8_safety_r",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 668,
      "width": 1420,
      "height": 89,
      "backgroundColor": "#fff3bf",
      "strokeColor": "#e67700",
      "strokeWidth": 1.5,
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "d8_safety_t",
      "x": 471.5,
      "y": 680.0,
      "width": 557,
      "height": 65,
      "text": "Safety Window\n- Keep MongoDB + Elasticsearch in READ-ONLY mode for 30 days after cutover\n- Rollback path preserved (switch clients back to legacy stores if needed)\n- Decommission legacy stores only after 30-day validation period",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "d8_annotations_r",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 777,
      "width": 1420,
      "height": 121,
      "backgroundColor": "#e7f5ff",
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "strokeWidth": 1.5,
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "d8_annotations_t",
      "x": 479.0,
      "y": 789.0,
      "width": 542,
      "height": 97,
      "text": "Workflow Properties:\n- Idempotent: re-running a batch is safe (upsert by (instrument_id, ts))\n- Resumable: workflow resumes after failures via Temporal checkpoints\n- Parallel: 16 workers migrate different date ranges simultaneously\n- Validated: spot-check 100 instruments x 30 days post-migration\n- Timezone-safe: dd-MM-yyyy strings converted to IST epoch microseconds",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "d8_benefits_r",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 913,
      "width": 1420,
      "height": 111,
      "backgroundColor": "#d3f9d8",
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "strokeWidth": 1.5,
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "d8_benefits_t",
      "x": 462.0,
      "y": 925.0,
      "width": 576,
      "height": 87,
      "text": "Benefits:\n- Zero user-visible downtime during migration\n- Zero data loss (validated by checksum per partition)\n- Rollback available for 30 days after cutover\n- Temporal handles retries, checkpointing, and visibility automatically",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    }
